                  Suppose you are given that <m>I_T(94,75) = 3.75</m> and <m>I_H(94,75) = 0.9</m>.  Use this given information and one other value from the table to estimate the value of <m>I(93.1,77)</m> using the linearization at <m>(94,75)</m>.  Using proper terminology and notation, explain your work and thinking.
